      • getJ2SEJarFiles

        public static java.lang.String[] getJ2SEJarFiles()
        Determine the classpath noted in wala.properties for J2SE standard libraries

        If wala.properties cannot be loaded, returns jar files in boot classpath.

        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if jar files cannot be discovered
        See Also:
        PlatformUtil.getBootClassPathJars()

      • getJ2EEJarFiles

        public static java.lang.String[] getJ2EEJarFiles()
        Returns:
        names of the Jar files holding J2EE libraries
        Throws:
